ut Davis out |magazine=Snooker Scene |pages=28-29 |publisher=Everton's News Agency |issue=April 2002}}</ref><br/>(Best of 19 frames)\n|-\n|  '''{{flagicon|ISL}} [[Kristj\u00e1n Helgason]] 10'''\u20139 {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Matthew Couch]]\n|  '''{{flagicon|ISL}} [[Kristj\u00e1n Helgason]] 10'''\u20135 {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Rod Lawler]]\n|  '''{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Stuart Bingham]] 10'''\u20137 {{flagicon|ISL}} [[Kristj\u00e1n Helgason]]\n|  '''{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Stuart Bingham]] 10'''\u20136 {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Nigel Bond]]\n|-\n|  '''{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Paul Wykes]] 10'''\u20135 {{flagicon|ENG}} Matthew Street\n|  '''{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Paul Wykes]] 10'''\u20134 {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Peter Lines]]\n|  '''{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Paul Wykes]] 10'''\u20138 {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Bradley Jones (snooker player)|Bradley Jones]]\n|  '''{{flagicon|WAL}} [[Dominic Dale]] 10'''\u20135 {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Paul Wykes]]\n|-\n|  '''{{flagicon|WAL}} [[Ryan Day (snooker player)|Ryan Day]] 5'''\u20131 {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Joe Johnson (snooker player)|Joe Johnson]](Johnson retired)\n|  '''{{flagicon|WAL}} [[Ryan Day (snooker player)|Ryan Day]] 10'''\u20138 {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Mark Davis (snooker player)|Mark Davis]]\n|  '''{{flagicon|SCO}} [[Marcus Campbell]] 10'''\u20139 {{flagicon|WAL}} [[Ryan Day (snooker player)|Ryan Day]]\n|  '''{{flagicon|WAL}} [[Anthony Davies]] 10'''\u20139 {{flagicon|SCO}} [[Marcus Campbell]]\n|-\n|  '''{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Mike Dunn (snooker player)|Mike Dunn]] 10'''\u20138 {{flagicon|IRE}} [[David McDonnell]]\n|  '''{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Mike Dunn (snooker player)|Mike Dunn]] 10'''\u20132 {{flagicon|WAL}} [[Lee Walker]]\n|  '''{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Mike Dunn (snooker player)|Mike Dunn]] 10'''\u20135 {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Dave Finbow]]\n|  '''{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Mike Dunn (snooker player)|Mike Dunn]] 10'''\u20139 {{flagicon|SCO}} [[Billy Snaddon]]\n|-\n|  '''{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Mark Selby]] 10'''\u20138 {{flagicon|BEL}} [[Bjorn Haneveer]]\n|  '''{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Mark Selby]] 10'''\u20136 {{flag